{"tid":2019630,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"匪徒要脅殺寵物逼阿里就範","createTime":"2020-05-16T12:03:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-16T13:14:27.000Z","uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e0eaa37357fa9f37c90912d04456defdd79e0657","tid":2019630,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T12:03:53.000Z","msg":"【Now Sports】熱刺球星阿里早前遭入屋行劫，更多案情曝光，最新消息指兩名匪徒曾要脅如果不交出財物，就會殺死阿里與女友的愛犬。<br />\n<br />\n英國《每日星報》報道指，兩名持刀匪徒進入阿里（Dele Alli）住所後，一度攻擊阿里，並要脅所有人按要求交出財物，否則會傷害他們；其後匪徒更威脅如果沒有人遵從，將會殺死阿里與其女友Ruby Mae的愛犬Uno。<br />\n<br />\n幸而最後所有人都無大礙，遭拳打導致嘴部受傷的阿里亦回到熱刺參加操練。倫敦警方發聲明證實案件仍在調查當中，尚未有人被捕：「警方在周三凌晨收到行劫報告，兩名男子劫走珠寶、手錶等貴重財物後逃走，事件中兩名男住客面部受輕傷，兩人均不需要入院治療，暫時沒有逮捕任何人，調查將會繼續。」<br />\n<br />\n而且阿里早前亦公開總值逾35萬鎊的失物名單，令賊人難以將贓物賣出套出。<br />\n<br />\n圖片來源 : Instagram圖片"},{"pid":"2e0fb333aadf22485e7a30eefe9aef884e579630","tid":2019630,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T12:04:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://66.media.tumblr.com/6660a8d067fe2aa76248fc491629224d/341d08b38d4529fd-f3/s250x400/477875c0bc14e6a2568d6250a8d8e218a9eb452f.gifv\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F66.media.tumblr.com%2F6660a8d067fe2aa76248fc491629224d%2F341d08b38d4529fd-f3%2Fs250x400%2F477875c0bc14e6a2568d6250a8d8e218a9eb452f.gifv&h=daf061fa&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d216370857a75f3ed816b80bdd23ff1cea8e7ade","tid":2019630,"uid":30081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T13:13:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.unrealengine.com/Diesel%2Fproductv2%2Funo%2Fhome%2FGameName_Store_Landscape_2560x1440-2560x1440-5195e8a3e06d672f97a1ee49ecea59027c14cae4.jpg?h=1080&amp;resize=1&amp;w=1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.unrealengine.com%2FDiesel%252Fproductv2%252Funo%252Fhome%252FGameName_Store_Landscape_2560x1440-2560x1440-5195e8a3e06d672f97a1ee49ecea59027c14cae4.jpg%3Fh%3D1080%26resize%3D1%26w%3D1920&h=34fd185b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"af9da92f7f05a7